channel.description:
Anybody who wishes to join the clan I am in on RuneScape you are more than welcome to join! All f2p and p2p are both welcome. We are an old friends chat from 2007 that turned into something larger. I would love to see some people join so we can have some nice chats.
T.S.S. stands for The Slayer Society.
You can join the chat by joining the clan chat " TSS " if that doesn't work try "THe Slayer Society" I forget which one it is xD
